extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em MoviesDatabbase], an Express website developed as a part of a fourth year project.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The database has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Movies:] !{data.movie_count}
      li #[strong Directors:] !{data.directors_count} 
      li #[strong Stars:] !{data.stars_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}